metadata.name: The Merge #1/22
metadata.description:
'The Merge' is released to commemorate the success of #EthereumMerge and to witness this historical event while being in NFT space for over 14 months.

This image is taken from one of my street photography series 'Stranger Things' #shotoniphone. With the reflection of the two people merging it resembles the theme and also creates an element of surprise for our viewers.
